{
  "name": "Review Reply Drafter — WorkflowStacks",
  "nodes": [
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## 💬 Review Reply Drafter\n\n**What it does:** reads customer reviews from your Google Sheet and drafts a personalized, on-brand reply for every review that doesn't have one yet — including careful, de-escalating replies to negative reviews. Drafts land in a `Drafted Replies` tab for your approval; nothing is ever sent automatically.\n\n### Setup (≈5 minutes)\n1. Make a Google Sheet with a tab named `Reviews` and these headers in row 1: **Customer Name**, **Rating**, **Review**, **Reply** (leave empty). Paste your reviews in (export them from Shopify, Judge.me, Loox, Amazon, or anywhere).\n2. Add a second empty tab named `Drafted Replies`.\n3. Open **Get reviews** → connect Google → pick your spreadsheet + the `Reviews` tab.\n4. Open **Draft reply (AI)** → add your OpenAI API key.\n5. Open **Save drafts** → same spreadsheet, `Drafted Replies` tab.\n6. Click **Execute workflow** — drafts appear, you approve & post them.\n\n💡 Edit the prompt in **Draft reply (AI)** to match your brand voice.\n\n— Free template from workflowstacks.com",
        "height": 620,
        "width": 460,
        "color": 5
      },
      "id": "b2c3d4e5-0001-4000-8000-000000000001",
      "name": "Setup instructions",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [-40, -180]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {},
      "id": "b2c3d4e5-0002-4000-8000-000000000002",
      "name": "When clicking Execute",
